    • Method Detail

      • getTokenSequenceNumber

        int getTokenSequenceNumber()
        Gets the token sequence number (aka GIDV) that distinguishes this token among others the users has.

        The token sequence number is an unsigned value ranging from 0x00 to 0x63 (i.e. 0 to 99).

        Returns:
        the users token sequence number
